@page "/case-studies"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<PageTitle>Case Studies - Zolv</PageTitle>

<section class="hero-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-heading" style="color: white;">Case studies</h2>
        <h3 class="section-subheading" style="color: white;">Delivery that stands up in real environments</h3>
        <p class="hero-description">
            We work with travel businesses that have real customers, real volume and real constraints.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-description">
            These case studies show how we approach complex platforms, integrations and long-term delivery — and what changed as a result.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="partnership-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-heading">We empower our clients to stay ahead — by fixing what actually holds them back</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
            Most of the value in travel technology doesn't come from brand-new ideas. It comes from removing friction, simplifying complexity 
            and making existing systems work harder.
        </p>
        <p class="section-description">That's where we focus.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="design-build-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h3 class="section-subheading">A few of our travel partners</h3>
        
        <div class="logos-grid" style="margin: 40px 0;">
            <span>Virgin Holidays</span>
            <span>HF Holidays</span>
            <span>CV Villas</span>
            <span>Monarch</span>
            <span>Kuoni</span>
            <span>Ramble Worldwide</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="partnership-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-heading">What our clients say</h2>
        <h3 class="section-subheading">Proof from people who have to live with the outcome</h3>
        
        <div class="testimonials">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <blockquote style="font-size: 20px; font-style: italic; color: var(--color-primary-purple);">
                    "Partnering with Zolv has inspired our travel services. Their solutions streamlined our booking process and enabled more personalised journeys."
                </blockquote>
                <p style="font-weight: 700; margin-top: 20px;">CEO, Virgin Holidays</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <blockquote style="font-size: 20px; font-style: italic; color: var(--color-primary-purple);">
                    "The new functionality has been really well received. We've seen a clear uplift in both sales and performance."
                </blockquote>
                <p style="font-weight: 700; margin-top: 20px;">Product Manager, HF Holidays</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <blockquote style="font-size: 20px; font-style: italic; color: var(--color-primary-purple);">
                    "The migration was a success thanks to Zolv's approach to teamwork. The new post-booking experience brought a fresh direction to our brand."
                </blockquote>
                <p style="font-weight: 700; margin-top: 20px;">Product Manager, Monarch</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="design-build-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Explore industry insights</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
            For a deeper look at how we think about platforms, integrations and delivery:
        </p>
        <a href="/insights" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore our insights</a>
    </div>
</section>